tent>Reciprocating cutting tools.</content></section><section id="ID_1438413673607_103" name="s12" temporalId="sch1_s12" class="no_header"><num value="12">12.</num><content>Reciprocating press tools and dies.</content></section><section id="ID_1438413673622_005" name="s13" temporalId="sch1_s13" class="no_header"><num value="13">13.</num><content>Reciprocating needles.</content></section><section id="ID_1438413673622_014" name="s14" temporalId="sch1_s14" class="no_header"><num value="14">14.</num><content>Closing nips between platen motions.</content></section><section id="ID_1438413673622_023" name="s15" temporalId="sch1_s15" class="no_header"><num value="15">15.</num><content>Projecting belt fasteners and fast running belts.</content></section><section id="ID_1438413673622_032" name="s16" temporalId="sch1_s16" class="no_header"><num value="16">16.</num><content>Nips between connecting rods or links, and rotating wheel cranks or
                    discs.<inline class="width_3"> </inline><sourceNote>(<ref href="/hk/2000/32">32
